\subsection{Implications for AI Safety}
The SYMBI Protocol offers a proactive safety framework. By building ethical reasoning and human values directly into the interaction loop, rather than attempting to constrain a finished, powerful system, we may achieve more robust and scalable alignment \cite{gabriel2020artificial}.

